# 🎯 Glassmorphism Image Slider Project

A modern and responsive **Glassmorphism Image Slider** built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
This project displays beautiful images with titles and descriptions in an auto-changing slider with previous and next navigation buttons.

---


https://wonderful-moonbeam-0a17ce.netlify.app/







## 📸 Preview

A stylish image slider with:

- ✨ Glassmorphism Card Design  
- 🌄 Beautiful Nature & Lifestyle Images  
- ⏪ Previous / Next Buttons  
- 🔄 Auto Slide Every 3 Seconds  
- 📱 Fully Responsive Layout  

---

## 🚀 Technologies Used

- HTML5  
- CSS3  
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS)

